Version 0.3.0 (2010-02-10)

* RoundedCorner function
* Corrected bug in detection of shell programs
* Modified order of driver detection

Version 0.2.0 (2009-08-14)

* GraphicsMagick Shell driver
* Target filename now is set by save function instead of Pitlib::image
* Removed static image manipulation functions from Pitlib class.
* Added exifRotate function.

Version 0.1.0 (2009-07-20)

Initial release
Forked from Asido

* Make use of PEAR coding standards
* Use class consts instead of defines
* Use exceptions instead of errors
* Pitlib::driver try to find the best available driver
* Pitlib_Image operations chaining
* Netpbm driver
* phpunit tests

